contentrichtext.text: '''Queensway''' may refer to: ==United Kingdom== *[[Queensway (Birmingham)]] *[[Queensway (London)]] *[[Queensway Tunnel]], in Merseyside *[[Queensway tube station]], in London *Queensway, [[Rochdale]], in Greater Manchester. *[[Queensway (Stevenage)]], a shopping centre *[[Queensway (retailer)]], a defunct furniture retailer ==Gibraltar== *[[Queensway (Gibraltar)]] ==Ontario, Canada== *[[Image:Ontario 417.svg|20px]] [[Queensway (Ottawa)]], a highway in Ottawa, incorporating part of provincial highway 417 and part of Ottawa highway 174 *[[Image:Ontario 3.svg|20px]] [[Queensway (Simcoe, Ontario)]], a section of Highway 3 in Simcoe *[[The Queensway (Toronto)|The Queensway]], the extension of Queen Street West in Toronto *[[Image:PRR20.PNG|20px]] Peel Regional Road 20, the portion of The Queensway in Peel Region *[[Image:York Regional Road 12.svg|20px]] [[York Regional Road 12]], in Georgina Township *[[Queensway-Humber Bay]] A neighbourhood in Toronto ==Hong Kong== *[[Queensway, Hong Kong]], an arterial route in the commercial district of Admiralty ==New Delhi, India== *The original name for the arterial road [[Janpath]] in Lutyen's Delhi. ==Singapore== *Queensway, a road in the [[Queenstown, Singapore|Queenstown]] area *[[Queensway Secondary School, Singapore]] ==United States== * [[Queensway (New York City)]], the alternative name of the [[Long Island Rail Road]] [[Rockaway Beach Branch]] ==See also== *[[Kingsway (disambiguation)]] {{Expand list|date=August 2008}} {{geodis}} [[Category:Lists of roads sharing the same title]]
